{
  "texts": [
    "\"I found the learning process with ChatGPT a bit confusing since it didn't provide any visuals for the ADAS functions.",
    "I had to read the text and figure out the location of the button.",
    "It would be easier if ChatGPT included images of the ADAS functions\". 2.",
    "\"I had a bit of trouble learning with ChatGPT because it didn't show me any pictures of the ADAS buttons; I only got written explanations.",
    "In my opinion, images can help to make learning easier."
